How do plants improve air quality? How do plants improve well-being? What is the number one killer of plants? What is the Plantline? Shipping Where does Neverland ship? How much does shipping cost? What is your return policy? How does the satisfaction guarantee work?
I've never grown a plant before. Is Neverland right for me? There’s no such thing as a black thumb. It’s normal for questions to arise such as: “How do I choose a plant? How much light does my plant need? How often do I have to water it? What happens if I forget? Is fertilizer necessary, and how often should I use it? How can I tell when I need to repot my plant? What kind of soil should I use? Why are the leaves turning brown, and where did these bugs come from?” If you’ve ever wondered about the answer to any of these questions, you’ve come to the right place.
